|\sqrt{x}-\sqrt{4}| = |\sqrt{x}-2|= |\frac{x-4}{\sqrt{x+2}}|= \frac{|x-4|}{|\sqrt{x}+2|}
|x-4|<\delta<1 \Rightarrow \frac{|x-4|}{|\sqrt{x}+2|}<\frac{\delta}{2}.
